Title: Here Kitty
Plot: Morgan works in a nursing home with a pet cat who only sleeps next to people if they are about to die - and does so with alarmingly accuracy. When it seems the cat has predicted her own death, Morgan, convinced she is about to die, fakes a seizure in order to get to House to have him diagnose her before it?s too late.
GuestStars: Judy Greer, Christopher Moynihan, Jennifer Crystal Foley, Whitney Cummings, Charlie Carter, Lorene Noh, Bobbin Bergstrom
